Change Log:
===========


---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version: 1.07 Wed 26-Aug-92        Jonathan Roach                

* Obtain sources from D.O.
* Implement auto-configuration
* Implement proper (RISC OS 3) removable media support for winnies
* Implement timed disc spin-down for power saving

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version: 1.14 Tue 12-Apr-94        Jonathan Roach                

Read-ahead and write-behind implemented.
...and debugged!
