Version: 1.08 Wed 02-Nov-94        Alan Glover                   

Add SCSIFS_FreeSpace64 to header file. No code change. Version number
incremented to 0.24.

(This definition is added ahead of the actual coding so that the Free
module knows which SWI to try before falling back to SCSIFS_FreeSpace)

